New release
===========

- run tests:
  $ ./run_tests.py all
- update VERSION and RELEASE_NOTES
- check README
- build new release and smoke check:
  $ ./setup.py sdist --formats=gztar,zip
- build new release and upload:
  $ ./setup.py sdist --formats=gztar,zip upload


PyPI setup
==========

$ cat ~/.pypirc
[server-login]
username:USERNAME
password:PASSWORD


